    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-05-17T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-05-17T04:00:00-05:00" n="730"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d730">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.516/5–1749: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister-Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clark</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Canton</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-05-17T17:00:00+08:00"
                            >May 17, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received May 17—10:17 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cantel 398. Central Bank today in connection financial problems otherwise
                        reported<note n="81" xml:id="d730fn81">Telegram Cantel No. 399, May 17, <ref
                            target="#pg_778">p. 778</ref>.</note> discussed with us proposed
                    monetary reform <pb facs="0785" n="775" xml:id="pg_775"/> plan predicated on US
                    dollars 100,000,000 loan to Chinese Govt for silver purchases. (See Cantel 372
                    [May 13], repeated Nanking 279, Shanghai 234.)</p>
                <p>We informed Central Bank that according Washington instructions US Govt has no
                    legal authority negotiate loan that nature.</p>
                <p>Recent decree Legislative Yuan requests Soong and Kung families contribute US
                    dollars 1,000,000,000 to national cause regarded by financial officials as
                    purely wishful thinking.</p>
                <p>Sent Dept; repeated Nanking 294, Shanghai 248.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clark</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
